(11, 'Python Data Types', 'python-data-types', '<h2 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 32px; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Built-in Data Types</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 1.2em; margin-bottom: 1.2em; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\">In programming, data type is an important concept.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 1.2em; margin-bottom: 1.2em; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\">Variables can store data of different types, and different types can do different things.</p><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 1.2em; margin-bottom: 1.2em; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\">Python has the following data types built-in by default, in these categories:</p><table class=\"w3-table\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; width: 1017.86px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><tbody style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><tr style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px 8px 8px 16px; vertical-align: top; width: 160px;\">Text Type:</td><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px; vertical-align: top;\"><code class=\"w3-codespan\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, &quot;courier new&quot;, monospace; font-size: 15.75px; color: crimson; background-color: rgba(222, 222, 222, 0.3);\">str</code></td></tr><tr style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px 8px 8px 16px; vertical-align: top;\">Numeric Types:</td><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px; vertical-align: top;\"><code class=\"w3-codespan\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, &quot;courier new&quot;, monospace; font-size: 15.75px; color: crimson; background-color: rgba(222, 222, 222, 0.3);\">int</code>,&nbsp;<code class=\"w3-codespan\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, &quot;courier new&quot;, monospace; font-size: 15.75px; color: crimson; background-color: rgba(222, 222, 222, 0.3);\">float</code>,&nbsp;<code class=\"w3-codespan\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, &quot;courier new&quot;, monospace; font-size: 15.75px; color: crimson; background-color: rgba(222, 222, 222, 0.3);\">complex</code></td></tr><tr style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px 8px 8px 16px; vertical-align: top;\">Sequence Types:</td><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px; vertical-align: top;\"><code class=\"w3-codespan\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, &quot;courier new&quot;, monospace; font-size: 15.75px; color: crimson; background-color: rgba(222, 222, 222, 0.3);\">list</code>,&nbsp;<code class=\"w3-codespan\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, &quot;courier new&quot;, monospace; font-size: 15.75px; color: crimson; background-color: rgba(222, 222, 222, 0.3);\">tuple</code>,&nbsp;<code class=\"w3-codespan\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, &quot;courier new&quot;, monospace; font-size: 15.75px; color: crimson; background-color: rgba(222, 222, 222, 0.3);\">range</code></td></tr><tr style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px 8px 8px 16px; vertical-align: top;\">Mapping Type:</td><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px; vertical-align: top;\"><code class=\"w3-codespan\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, &quot;courier new&quot;, monospace; font-size: 15.75px; color: crimson; background-color: rgba(222, 222, 222, 0.3);\">dict</code></td></tr><tr style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px 8px 8px 16px; vertical-align: top;\">Set Types:</td><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px; vertical-align: top;\"><code class=\"w3-codespan\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, &quot;courier new&quot;, monospace; font-size: 15.75px; color: crimson; background-color: rgba(222, 222, 222, 0.3);\">set</code>,&nbsp;<code class=\"w3-codespan\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, &quot;courier new&quot;, monospace; font-size: 15.75px; color: crimson; background-color: rgba(222, 222, 222, 0.3);\">frozenset</code></td></tr><tr style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px 8px 8px 16px; vertical-align: top;\">Boolean Type:</td><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px; vertical-align: top;\"><code class=\"w3-codespan\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, &quot;courier new&quot;, monospace; font-size: 15.75px; color: crimson; background-color: rgba(222, 222, 222, 0.3);\">bool</code></td></tr><tr style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px 8px 8px 16px; vertical-align: top;\">Binary Types:</td><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px; vertical-align: top;\"><code class=\"w3-codespan\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, &quot;courier new&quot;, monospace; font-size: 15.75px; color: crimson; background-color: rgba(222, 222, 222, 0.3);\">bytes</code>,&nbsp;<code class=\"w3-codespan\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, &quot;courier new&quot;, monospace; font-size: 15.75px; color: crimson; background-color: rgba(222, 222, 222, 0.3);\">bytearray</code>,&nbsp;<code class=\"w3-codespan\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, &quot;courier new&quot;, monospace; font-size: 15.75px; color: crimson; background-color: rgba(222, 222, 222, 0.3);\">memoryview</code></td></tr><tr style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px 8px 8px 16px; vertical-align: top;\">None Type:</td><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px; vertical-align: top;\"><code class=\"w3-codespan\" style=\