erit; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, &quot;courier new&quot;, monospace; font-size: 15.75px; color: crimson; background-color: rgba(222, 222, 222, 0.3);\">-</code>&nbsp;has the same precedence, and therefor we evaluate the expression from left to right:</p><div class=\"w3-code notranslate pythonHigh\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, &quot;courier new&quot;, monospace; width: auto; background-color: rgb(21, 32, 43); color: white; padding: 8px 12px; border-left: 4px solid rgb(40, 44, 52); overflow-wrap: break-word; margin-top: 16px !important; margin-bottom: 16px !important;\"><span class=\"pythonkeywordcolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">print</span>(<span class=\"pythonnumbercolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\">5</span>&nbsp;+&nbsp;<span class=\"pythonnumbercolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\">4</span>&nbsp;-&nbsp;<span class=\"pythonnumbercolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\">7</span>&nbsp;+&nbsp;<span class=\"pythonnumbercolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\">3</span>)<br></div><a target=\"_blank\" class=\"w3-btn w3-margin-bottom\" href=\"https://www.w3schools.com/python/trypython.asp?filename=demo_precedence_same\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgb(76, 175, 80); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: none; display: inline-block; padding: 6px 18px; vertical-align: middle; overflow: hidden; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; text-wrap: nowrap; user-select: none; border-radius: 5px; font-size: 17px; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 16px !important;\">Run example »</a></div>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-06-15 11:54:26');
