(27, 'Python - List Methods', 'python-list-methods', '<h2 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 32px; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">List Methods</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 1.2em; margin-bottom: 1.2em; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\">Python has a set of built-in methods that you can use on lists.</p><table class=\"ws-table-all notranslate\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; width: 1017.86px; border: 1px solid rgb(204, 204, 204); margin: 20px 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 15px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><tbody style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><tr style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(221, 221, 221);\"><th style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px 8px 8px 16px; vertical-align: top;\">Method</th><th style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px; vertical-align: top;\">Description</th></tr><tr style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); background-color: rgb(231, 233, 235);\"><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px 8px 8px 16px; vertical-align: top;\"><a href=\"https://www.w3schools.com/python/ref_list_append.asp\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: inherit;\">append()</a></td><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px; vertical-align: top;\">Adds an element at the end of the list</td></tr><tr style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(221, 221, 221);\"><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px 8px 8px 16px; vertical-align: top;\"><a href=\"https://www.w3schools.com/python/ref_list_clear.asp\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: inherit;\">clear()</a></td><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px; vertical-align: top;\">Removes all the elements from the list</td></tr><tr style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border-bottom-widt