b(255, 255, 255);\">:&nbsp;</span><span class=\"pythonstringcolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\">\"Ford\"</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">,</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span class=\"pythonnumbercolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class=\"pythonstringcolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\">\"model\"</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">:&nbsp;</span><span class=\"pythonstringcolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\">\"Mustang\"</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">,</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span class=\"pythonnumbercolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class=\"pythonstringcolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\">\"year\"</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">:&nbsp;</span><span class=\"pythonnumbercolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\">1964</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span class=\"pythonnumbercolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\"></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">}</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">x = thisdict[</span><span class=\"pythonstringcolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: brown;\">\"model\"</span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">]</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><span class=\"pythonnumbercolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\"></span></span></div><a target=\"_blank\" class=\"w3-btn w3-margin-bottom\" href=\"https://www.w3schools.com/python/trypython.asp?filename=demo_dictionary_access\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgb(76, 175, 80); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: none; display: inline-b