or: rgb(76, 175, 80); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: none; display: inline-block; padding: 6px 18px; vertical-align: middle; overflow: hidden; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; text-wrap: nowrap; user-select: none; border-radius: 5px; font-size: 17px; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 16px !important;\">Try it Yourself »</a></div>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-06-15 13:35:17');
