bercolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\">6</span>:<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><span class=\"pythonnumbercolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\"></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"pythonkeywordcolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">print</span>(i)<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\"><span class=\"pythonnumbercolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\"></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"pythonkeywordcolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">if</span>&nbsp;i ==&nbsp;<span class=\"pythonnumbercolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\">3</span>:<br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span class=\"pythonkeywordcolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: mediumblue;\">break</span><br style=\"box-sizing: inherit;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;i +=&nbsp;<span class=\"pythonnumbercolor\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: red;\">1</span><br></div><a target=\"_blank\" class=\"w3-btn w3-margin-bottom\" href=\"https://www.w3schools.com/python/trypython.asp?filename=demo_while_break\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; background-color: rgb(76, 175, 80); color: rgb(255, 255, 255); border: none; display: inline-block; padding: 6px 18px; vertical-align: middle; overflow: hidden; text-align: center; cursor: pointer; text-wrap: nowrap; user-select: none; border-radius: 5px; font-size: 17px; font-family: &quot;Source Sans Pro&quot;, sans-serif; margin-bottom: 16px !important;\">Try it Yourself »</a></div><div><h2 style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-size: 32px; font-family: &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; margin-top: 10px; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 0px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">The continue Statement</h2><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 1.2em; margin-bottom: 1.2em; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif;\">With the&nbsp;<span class=\"w3-codespan\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-family: Consolas, Menlo, &quot;courier new&quot;, monospace; font-size: 15.75px;