m-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); background-color: rgb(231, 233, 235);\"><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px 8px 8px 16px; vertical-align: top;\"><a href=\"https://www.w3schools.com/python/ref_list_extend.asp\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: inherit;\">extend()</a></td><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px; vertical-align: top;\">Add the elements of a list (or any iterable), to the end of the current list</td></tr><tr style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(221, 221, 221);\"><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px 8px 8px 16px; vertical-align: top;\"><a href=\"https://www.w3schools.com/python/ref_list_index.asp\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: inherit;\">index()</a></td><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px; vertical-align: top;\">Returns the index of the first element with the specified value</td></tr><tr style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); background-color: rgb(231, 233, 235);\"><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px 8px 8px 16px; vertical-align: top;\"><a href=\"https://www.w3schools.com/python/ref_list_insert.asp\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: inherit;\">insert()</a></td><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px; vertical-align: top;\">Adds an element at the specified position</td></tr><tr style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(221, 221, 221);\"><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px 8px 8px 16px; vertical-align: top;\"><a href=\"https://www.w3schools.com/python/ref_list_pop.asp\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: inherit;\">pop()</a></td><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px; vertical-align: top;\">Removes the element at the specified position</td></tr><tr style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); background-color: rgb(231, 233, 235);\"><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px 8px 8px 16px; vertical-align: top;\"><a href=\"https://www.w3schools.com/python/ref_list_remove.asp\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: inherit;\">remove()</a></td><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px; vertical-align: top;\">Removes the first item with the specified value</td></tr><tr style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(221, 221, 221);\"><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px 8px 8px 16px; vertical-align: top;\"><a href=\"https://www.w3schools.com/python/ref_list_reverse.asp\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: inherit;\">reverse()</a></td><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px; vertical-align: top;\">Reverses the order of the list</td></tr><tr style=\"box-sizing: inherit; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: rgb(221, 221, 221); background-color: rgb(231, 233, 235);\"><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px 8px 8px 16px; vertical-align: top;\"><a href=\"https://www.w3schools.com/python/ref_list_sort.asp\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; color: inherit;\">sort()</a></td><td style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 8px; vertical-align: top;\">Sorts the list</td></tr></tbody></table><div class=\"w3-panel w3-note\" style=\"box-sizing: inherit; padding: 16px 32px; margin: 24px -32px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 204); border-left: none; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Verdana, sans-serif; font-size: 15px;\"><p style=\"box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 1em; margin-bottom: 1em;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: inherit; font-weight: bolder;\">Note:</span>&nbsp;Python does not have built-in support for Arrays, but Python Lists can be used instead.</p></div>', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, '2023-06-15 15:53:52');
